sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Codex["Codex CLI"]
    participant Prompt[".codex/prompts/<br/>arckit.requirements.md"]
    participant Script[".arckit/scripts/bash/<br/>create-project.sh"]
    participant Template[".arckit/templates/<br/>requirements-template.md"]
    participant Output["projects/001-name/<br/>ARC-001-REQ-v1.0.md"]
    
    User->>Codex: /prompts:arckit.requirements NHS system
    
    Codex->>Prompt: Load prompt file
    Prompt-->>Codex: Instructions + prerequisites
    
    Codex->>Script: bash create-project.sh --json
    Note over Script: Approval prompt<br/>(unless --auto)
    Script-->>Codex: {"path": "projects/001-nhs-system/"}
    
    Codex->>Template: Read template file
    Template-->>Codex: Template content
    
    Codex->>Codex: Populate template with<br/>project context
    
    Codex->>Output: Write document via Write tool
    Output-->>Codex: File written
    
    Codex-->>User: Summary of generated document<br/>(not full content)
